{"tid":446883,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[承諾撚]有無人好重視承諾?","createTime":"2017-10-24T17:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T16:27:59.000Z","uid":153493,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4436a67f4cdf0ac27732eab34fb4d05c1c2a1c84","tid":446883,"uid":153493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:06:36.000Z","msg":"由細到大<br />\n大家都會被長輩教導過<br />\n做人一定要有口齒<br />\n&quot;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講過陷家剷就一定要陷家剷&quot;<br />\n</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但事實上好似得o靚坤一個<br />\n先係最遵守諾言個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無印象親人親戚都會鳩吹呃鳩你<br />\n話會戒煙食少d嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話會帶你出去玩<br />\n帶你去馬爾代夫嫁啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n甚至人大左<br />\n互相放飛機嘅次數<br />\n就好似會隨住年齡愈大愈多<br />\n反而愈細個先可以愈守口齒咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己無點放過人飛機<br />\n講過嘅說話會好重視死都要做到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但有無人同我一樣<br />\n重視同遵守承諾嘅同時<br />\n愈黎愈灰鳩個心愈黎愈冷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6fd1b17a995f812feb61c94d0cfb104b756d13","tid":446883,"uid":79645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:09:24.000Z","msg":"經常比人放飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60eb51ef865a79b00c7cf3c31f728cb0ecb19e28","tid":446883,"uid":123969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:09:45.000Z","msg":"記得就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e55ff84d000c707b0c7541bfa4c671efda4d26","tid":446883,"uid":70135,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:11:35.000Z","msg":"應承左ex每年生日都第一個同講生日快樂<br />\n今年第七年"},{"pid":"5a1102f34f5e9aee8fd9c17d8c7ceae7ab127d45","tid":446883,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:12:06.000Z","msg":"社會唔鼓勵 好似係"},{"pid":"d44302fa124e379163648e22c8d475bbd2fc31b0","tid":446883,"uid":97299,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:12:38.000Z","msg":"一諾千金，做唔到就唔好承諾<br />\n凡係承諾，都要負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71a5ca0bbad907d46fb68d47825b3e7f054b77a","tid":446883,"uid":89402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:31:42.000Z","msg":"講就易<br />\n做真係難ga <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a476cf4051e29f01544c90c059801ebd4da1e0","tid":446883,"uid":7103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:40:06.000Z","msg":"當人被許下一個冇兌現到嘅承諾時，就會變得唔重視承諾"},{"pid":"0bde71e47e08f63e354f5657f95b028d5a09edf2","tid":446883,"uid":124491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:41:08.000Z","msg":"唔好遲到5分鍾就無限放大我不守承諾就ok鳥"},{"pid":"4cee831dfffcc2ece33f9abab822f20