ssets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拖拖下無左件事。第一次去日本玩係差唔多十幾年後自己開始返工揾錢自己去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCLS COMPANY <br />\n我都試過<br />\n細個個陣細姨姨話搵日帶我同我哥<br />\n去篤桌球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原本聽到真係好開心<br />\n事後篤閪咩閪都未閪篤過<br />\n我心諗你唔會做就咪撚講得咁逼真<br />\n咁閪口響呃鳩你個姪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105b07bb2cba88a669d4b63ac40da29f0242559e","tid":446883,"uid":92456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:47:59.000Z","msg":"人大咗就知承諾係好隨便嘅嘢"},{"pid":"3d739847a544fb3864e738b178ba57f1331874bd","tid":446883,"uid":153493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人比再多既承諾你 都敵唔過狗公</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n狗公同黑警都要死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要係絕子絕孫個種陷家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:前後比過兩個ex帽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但只係關係出軌唔係肉體上出軌"},{"pid":"cfa0fd0cb392e579556f9b0063ff31b71f4a5329","tid":446883,"uid":136902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:59:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由細到大<br />\n大家都會被長輩教導過<br />\n做人一定要有口齒<br />\n&quot;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講過陷家剷就一定要陷家剷&quot;<br />\n</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但事實上好似得o靚坤一個<br />\n先係最遵守諾言個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無印象親人親戚都會鳩吹呃鳩你<br />\n話會戒煙食少d嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話會帶你出去玩<br />\n帶你去馬爾代夫嫁啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n甚至人大左<br />\n互相放飛機嘅次數<br />\n就好似會隨住年齡愈大愈多<br />\n反而愈細個先可以愈守口齒咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己無點放過人飛機<br />\n講過嘅說話會好重視死都要做到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但有無人同我一樣<br />\n重視同遵守承諾嘅同時<br />\n愈黎愈灰鳩個心愈黎愈冷<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我從來唔講大話又好守承諾，所以成日搞到好多朋友dead air，無哂面，好多人都同我做唔到朋友，搞到朋友好小。<br />\n<br />\n因為好守承諾所以唔會亂承諾人，搞到flirt女都flirt唔到，追唔到女，就連係屋企都成日嘈，細個老豆叫我應承佢自己溫書，我唔應承，之後打到斷左兩枝地拖棍，miss迫我默書重默到合格為止，佢比曬機會我出貓都唔出，默到夜晚10點幾，都默唔識，默到好似我罰miss留堂咁，之後佢半放棄左我<br />\n<br />\n出黎做野唔呃人，下場唔講啦<br />\n<br />\n所以你確定咁真係好？我以上都係真事。。。同時覺得自己係on9仔"},{"pid":"87b4b9a85143e06924ddc199f245ee2627e84140","tid":446883,"uid":145310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:50:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid"